1. *Obzir* uzimajući na njegovu situaciju, moramo mu pomoći. (Taking into account his situation, we must help him.)

2. On je sa *obzirom* na to što je uradio, zaslužio da bude kažnjen. (He, with regard to what he did, deserved to be punished.)

3. On je dobio *obzir* od strane sudije. (He got consideration from the judge.)

4. Njegov advokat je tražio da mu se pruži *obzir*. (His lawyer asked for him to be given consideration.)

5. Njegov obzir je bio uspešan. (His consideration was successful.)